import axios from 'axios'; const BomDC = ({ open, proyect, navigation }) => { const [part, setPart] = useState({ p_clips: '', p_black: '', p_red: '', p_cable: '', p_female: '', p_male: '', p_solar: '', p_bolts: '', p_star: '', p_nut: '', p_ilsco: '', p_bare: '', p_burndy: '', p_servit: '', p_wire: '', p_mc: '', p_plastic: '', }); const [order, setOrder] = useState({ o_clips: '', o_black: '', o_red: '', o_cable: '', o_female: '', o_male: '', o_solar: '', o_bolts: '', o_star: '', o_nut: '', o_ilsco: '', o_bare: '', o_burndy: '', o_servit: '', o_wire: '', o_mc: '', o_plastic: '', }); const { p_clips, p_black, p_red, p_cable, p_female, p_male, p_solar, p_bolts, p_star, p_nut, p_ilsco, p_bare, p_burndy, p_servit, p_wire, p_mc, p_plastic } = part; const { o_clips, o_black, o_red, o_cable, o_female, o_male, o_solar, o_bolts, o_star, o_nut, o_ilsco, o_bare, o_burndy, o_servit, o_wire, o_mc, o_plastic } = order; const newProyect = async () => { try { let res = await axios({ method: "post", url: "http://localhost:8001/api/dc", data: { id: proyect.id, clips_p: clips_p, clips_o: clips_o, black_p: black_p, black_o: black_o, red_p: red_p, red_o: red_o, cable_p: cable_p, cable_o: cable_o, female_p: female_p, female_o: female_o, male_p: male_p, male_o: male_o, solar_p: solar_p, solar_o: solar_o, bolts_p: bolts_p, bolts_o: bolts_o, star_p: star_p, star_o: star_o, nut_p: nut_p, nut_o: nut_o, ilsco_p: ilsco_p, ilsco_o: ilsco_o, bare_p: bare_p, bare_o: bare_o, burndy_p: burndy_p, burndy_o: burndy_o, servit_p: servit_p, servit_o: servit_o, wire_p: wire_p, wire_o: wire_o, mc_p: mc_p, mc_o: mc_o, plastic_p: plastic_p, plastic_o: plastic_o, }, config: { headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" } } }); navigation.navigate('HOME'); } catch (error) { console.log('New Proyecy Error: ' + error.message); } }; return (
